WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:11.280
Economic interdependence and globalization connect countries through trade creating complex

00:11.280 --> 00:13.760
global supply chains.

00:13.760 --> 00:20.080
This reliance is vital for economic development as global trade opens new markets, attracts

00:20.080 --> 00:23.080
investment, and fosters innovation.

00:23.080 --> 00:28.120
Together, they enhance living standards worldwide.

00:28.120 --> 00:34.200
Economic interdependence and globalization economic interdependence is the mutual reliance

00:34.200 --> 00:41.160
between countries for goods, services, and resources enhanced by globalization.

00:41.160 --> 00:47.880
This has created complex global supply chains and increased economic integration.

00:47.880 --> 00:53.720
Economic interdependence, economic interdependence means countries are connected through trade

00:53.720 --> 00:57.720
where one nation's economic health can impact others.

00:57.720 --> 01:01.000
Now this interconnectedness can enhance stability.

01:01.000 --> 01:05.680
It also creates vulnerabilities if a country's economy falters.

01:05.680 --> 01:12.040
The role of global trade and economic development, global trade is vital for economic development,

01:12.040 --> 01:17.720
allowing countries to access new markets, acquire advanced technology, and attract foreign

01:17.720 --> 01:19.040
investment.

01:19.040 --> 01:24.840
It also drives innovation and enhances living standards by offering consumers a wider

01:24.840 --> 01:28.760
variety of goods and services.

01:28.760 --> 01:34.800
Access to markets, global trade allows countries to sell their products to a larger international

01:34.800 --> 01:36.400
market.

01:36.400 --> 01:44.120
This access to global markets can lead to increased production, higher revenues, and economic growth.

01:44.120 --> 01:51.520
In conclusion, economic interdependence and globalization foster growth and innovation.

01:51.520 --> 01:58.080
By engaging in global trade, countries can harness their strengths and adapt to challenges.

01:58.080 --> 02:03.400
This interconnectedness supports a more resilient and prosperous global economy.

